OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStop and search: Ethnic    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fminorities unfairly        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftargeted by police -       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Police need to end the overuse of stops
OL,6, and searches on black and ethnic       
OL,7, minorities, a watchdog has said.       
OL,9,FThe Independent Office for Police      
OL,10,FConduct is calling for guidelines that 
OL,11,Fprotect minorities from being stopped  
OL,12,Fdue to stereotypes and racial bias.    
OL,14,FIts report raised the case of a black  
OL,15,Fboy who said he was searched more than 
OL,16,F60 times between the ages of 14 and 16.
OL,18,FSearches handled insensitively could   
OL,19,Fleave people "humiliated and           
OL,20,Fvictimised", it said.                  
